<li id="cite_note-Wilkinson2017-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Wilkinson2017_4-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Wilkinson2017_4-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Wilkinson, Dominic, et al. (2017). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.academia.edu/33790626/THE_CHARLIE_GARD_CASE_BRITISH_AND_AMERICAN_APPROACHES_TO_COURT_RESOLUTION_OF_DISPUTES_OVER_MEDICAL_DECISIONS">"The Charlie Gard Case: British and American approaches to court resolution of disputes over medical decisions"</a>, <i>Journal of Perinatology</i>, courtesy of academia.edu.</span>
