<li id="cite_note-GOSH_Position_Statement_24_July-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-GOSH_Position_Statement_24_July_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-GOSH_Position_Statement_24_July_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-GOSH_Position_Statement_24_July_5-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-GOSH_Position_Statement_24_July_5-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.gosh.nhs.uk/news/latest-press-releases/gosh-position-statement-issued-high-court-24-july-2017">"GOSH Position Statement 24 July"</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=GOSH+Position+Statement+24+July&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gosh.nhs.uk%2Fnews%2Flatest-press-releases%2Fgosh-position-statement-issued-high-court-24-july-2017&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACharlie+Gard+case" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-independent_7861531-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-independent_7861531_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-independent_7861531_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-independent_7861531_6-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-independent_7861531_6-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation news cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.independent.co.uk/voices/charlie-gard-gosh-hirano-would-he-have-survived-a7861531.html">"Would Charlie Gard really have survived if he'd been treated sooner? Here's the sad truth"</a>. <i>The Independent</i>. 26 July 2017<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 July</span> 2017</span>. <q>Dr Hirano had never physically assessed Charlie nor had he had sight of his medical records and investigations, including the second opinions of doctors from outside GOSH.</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Independent&amp;rft.atitle=Would+Charlie+Gard+really+have+survived+if+he%27d+been+treated+sooner%3F+Here%27s+the+sad+truth&amp;rft.date=2017-07-26&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fvoices%2Fcharlie-gard-gosh-hirano-would-he-have-survived-a7861531.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACharlie+Gard+case" class="Z3988"></span></span>
